{{Quote|Best larvae in the Outer Rim Territories.|Ebenn Q3 Baobab praises Buzzee's larvae dishes in his guide book|<ref name="GPB&TG" />}}
'''Buzzee's''' was the name of a [[Restaurant/Legends|restaurant]] that was located in [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]] [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] during the reign of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. The [[Human/Legends|Human]] scholar [[Ebenn Q3 Baobab/Legends|Ebenn Q3 Baobab]] claimed that the [[Foodstuff/Legends|food]] at Buzzee's, all of which was [[Insect/Legends|insect]]-based, was unique and reasonably priced in the ''[[Galactic Phrase Book & Travel Guide]]'' he authored in [[6 ABY/Legends|6 ABY]]. Baobab also declared in the [[Book/Legends|book]] that the [[Larva/Legends|larvae]] served at the restaurant were the best available in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]] and included the establishment in a list of what he thought were the finest eateries in Mos Eisley.<ref name="GPB&TG" />

==Behind the scenes==
Buzzee's was first mentioned in the [[Galactic Phrase Book & Travel Guide (real-life book)|''Galactic Phrase Book & Travel Guide'']], a book written by [[Ben Burtt]] that was released in [[2001]].<ref name="GPB&TG" />

